imdb.plot outline: Wicca Please is the code name for a Spiritual Detective Agency based in Los Angeles that protect the world from mischievous mayhem and malevolent mojo. These hired magik-guns, vigilantes or heroes, work for the CIA, FBI, LAPD, rich folks, and everyday people who need help.
